		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">SaucJedi wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I'm really willing to remove it, but in the best possible way... Biggest problem is that I don't really know where and how it's really attached at MB. I see that there are some solder points, but it feels very sturdy for just those little solder points... Is it also glued or something?</div>
<br />
<br />
<br />"little" soldering points?!?!
<br />
<br />There are 4 LARGE ones for the chassis and 5 decent sized ones for the signal/power connections.  All 9 of those massive solder points with half of them sinking to the ground plane is what makes it so sturdy and difficult to desolder.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


